snippet.title: v6.2 The Chrono and the Hare Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd is ascending to v6.2 The Chrono and the Hare!
New SP battlesuit Chrono Navi for Ai Hyperion Λ debuts!
Story Chapter XXXIII and event Honkai Salvation Log to be released! Stay tuned!
